criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Fresh cadavers;

          -  Age> 18 years;

          -  Height between 150cm and 190cm;

          -  Any gender.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Corpses with severe spinal deformity;

          -  Known history of lumbar spine surgery;

          -  Scars suggestive of large anatomical manipulations of the lumbar region;

          -  Corpses with BMI> 35 kg / m².
